pageTitle: Malden Catholic: Alumni in Military Service
textBeforeTable: For updates, please contact Br. Ed Bozzo, CFX in the Malden Catholic Office of Institutional Advancement: 99 Crystal Street; Malden, MA 02148. Email: bozzoe@maldencatholic.org Aware that our list is incomplete, we are publishing it now on this website in hopes of stimulating input from our constituency. Please inform us of alumni who should be on our list. Help us, too, if you can fill in those entries in our list which lack the rank or branch of service. Thank you. We also welcome information on Girls Catholic alumnae who served. Since 2006, the Office of Institutional Advancement has been creating a list of Malden Catholic Alumni who have served in various branches of the United States military. Some of this information came from veterans themselves, or relatives and friends, some from research in early MC yearbooks, issues of the Hi-Lite which in the 1940s carried news of graduates in the service, issues of MC alumni newspapers and obituaries.
